        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(search): keep skills all tab on approved recommended ranking",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Keeps the `/skills` **All** tab on recommended discovery ranking instead of silently falling back to `updatedAt` ordering when recommendation scores are missing or stale.\n- Leaves **Recently updated** as the explicit `updatedAt desc` sort only.\n- Excludes pending-review, suspicious, and other non-public items from public browse/search, while still showing the last approved public version when a newer version is pending review.\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [x] `bunx vitest run` on touched Convex tests (`publicBrowse`, `listPublicPageV4`, `publicListCursor`, `packageCatalog`, `search`)\n- [x] `git diff --check`\n- [x] `bun run ci:static`\n- [x] `bun run ci:unit`",
